(264781, 8704, 262694, 'Masroor', 559, '', 1335779904, '[QUOTE=suuch_baat;262694]The Lubairs flocks move with wind storms so watch wind direction and cluster of big trees. Shooting Lubairs flying just before sunset on returning flocks near big trees is great fun as Lubairs come very fast and high only come to your range outside the trees if you are ready and well camoflagued....\n\n\n\nHaripur/Abbottabad valley are also great place to be in both harvesting seasons fall & spring.[/QUOTE]\n\nYes Dear You are Quite Right.', 1, 1, '39.45.199.34', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
