(269408, 8928, 269069, 'AK47', 162, '', 1337488562, 'Overall, it was a tie. NO winner, NO loser, no 100/90, 100/50 edge of one over another.\n\nAll shots were in black, and both had equally many shots out of black area during the practise shots. Score was 5 points more to the Caracal from one shooter, 6 points more to the Glock by our second shooter. Let''s not dramatize anything like "one thing shot the crap out of another thing".\n\nThere was no so-called "spray" of rounds by anything here GF bro. Glocks polygonal barrel is the reason of it''s better groupings comparatively, whereas polygynol barrel was not preferred by Caracal designer due to it''s own benefits, that''s all. Now you can dramatize it into any direction, the point, however, is, that a 75K handgun gave the other one a good run out there yesterday and they both performed well enough.\n\nKudus to our brethren for the arrangements. Let''s stick to the fun side of it.\n\nAnd in either case, as far as both guns are concerned, credit goes to origins in Austria.\n\n\nRegards.', 1, 1, '182.177.18.200', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
